resources.description: Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and INSPIRE theme register, INSPIRE feature concept dictionary

description: This alignment contains semantic mappings between EuroVoc and INSPIRE (INSPIRE feature concept dictionary and INSPIRE theme register). The total number of mappings in the dataset amounts to 84  including 14  "exactMatch", 10 "broadMatch",  14  "narrowMatch" and 16 "relatedMatch".
